<h2 id="invite-needed">You're nearly there...</h2>

<div class="ui attached red message">
  <div class="header">
    <i class="frown icon"></i> Bad News
  </div>
  <ul>
    <li>For the moment, you must <strong><u>receive an invite</u></strong> to use Tcal.</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="ui bottom attached green message">
  <div class="header">
    <i class="smile icon"></i> Good News
  </div>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong><u>You are on the list!</u></strong>
      Keep an eye on your <em><%= current_user.email %></em> inbox. You should receive an email within the next day!
    </li>
    <li>If you want to get in faster, you can also <strong><u>ask a friend</u></strong> to send you one of their <%= User::MAX_INVITES %> invites.</li>
    <li>Liking <a href="https://www.facebook.com/tcaldotme" target="_blank">our Facebook page</a> below may help too!</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="fb-like"
  data-href="https://www.facebook.com/tcaldotme"
  data-width="330"
  data-layout="standard"
  data-action="like"
  data-size="small"
  data-show-faces="true"
  data-share="true"></div>
